---
title: Hawaiian-Inspired Rice Bowls with Bacon and Pineapple
description: Prepare your taste buds for this pork stir fry with a Hawaiian pineapple twist! Green onions, broccoli, carrots and corn round out this one-pan wonder!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hawaiian-inspired-rice-bowls-6db6c0cb.jpg
